title: Second Monthly Hack Night
description:
Hang out, talk shop, get help on your projects. We're focused on open source stuff, but that's not a rule, just a priority. Come work in the Forge space.

No speaker, no sponsor except Forge, and no food provided. Bring food or drink if you want, bring a laptop if you need it to work, and come hang out and hack!

This is the second hack night of the monthly two.

title: React Utah Meetup
description:
Welcome
Come join us for some networking, food, and presentations!
Meetups are a great way to connect with the community and learn from each other.

Speaker: Informal hack night
We will just get together and have some good conversations and networking, if you have something you want to share the podium will be open for more lightning style presentations if anyone is inclined, otherwise come work on a side project, ask for advice, input, etc...

Remote Link: https://meet.google.com/uvo-zsre-min

Dinner: No dinner will be provided this month

Want to Present? You do not have to be an expert! Speaker Sign Up Form

Sponsors
Sponsors make this whole thing possible, free, and fun! We would love your help! If your company would like to help sponsor the meetup enabling us to continue delivering a great community event reach out to Mike North on Meetup or on Slack.
